        this.onMessage(byteBuffer);
    }
    
    public final void onWebsocketOpen(final WebSocket webSocket, final Handshakedata handshakedata) {
        this.startConnectionLostTimer();
        this.onOpen((ServerHandshake)handshakedata);
        this.connectLatch.countDown();
    }
    
    public final void onWriteDemand(final WebSocket webSocket) {
    }
    
    public void reconnect() {
        this.reset();
        this.connect();
    }
    
    public boolean reconnectBlocking() throws InterruptedException {
        this.reset();
        return this.connectBlocking();
    }
    
    public String removeHeader(final String s) {
        if (this.headers == null) {
            return null;
        }
        return (String)this.headers.remove((Object)s);
    }
    
    public void run() {
        try {
            final boolean prepareSocket = this.prepareSocket();
            this.socket.setTcpNoDelay(this.isTcpNoDelay());
            this.socket.setReuseAddress(this.isReuseAddr());
            if (!this.socket.isConnected()) {
                InetSocketAddress unresolved;
                if (this.dnsResolver == null) {
                    unresolved = InetSocketAddress.createUnresolved(this.uri.getHost(), this.getPort());
                }
                else {
                    unresolved = new InetSocketAddress(this.dnsResolver.resolve(this.uri), this.getPort());
                }
                this.socket.connect((SocketAddress)unresolved, this.connectTimeout);
            }
            if (prepareSocket && "wss".equals((Object)this.uri.getScheme())) {
                this.upgradeSocketToSSL();
            }
            if (this.socket instanceof SSLSocket) {
                final SSLSocket sslSocket = (SSLSocket)this.socket;
                final SSLParameters sslParameters = sslSocket.getSSLParameters();
                this.onSetSSLParameters(sslParameters);
                sslSocket.setSSLParameters(sslParameters);
            }
            final InputStream inputStream = this.socket.getInputStream();
            this.ostream = this.socket.getOutputStream();
            this.sendHandshake();
            (this.writeThread = new Thread((Runnable)new WebsocketWriteThread(this))).start();
            final byte[] array = new byte[16384];
            try {
                while (!this.isClosing() && !this.isClosed()) {
                    final int read = inputStream.read(array);
                    if (read == -1) {
                        break;
                    }
                    this.engine.decode(ByteBuffer.wrap(array, 0, read));
                }
                this.engine.eot();
            }
            catch (final RuntimeException ex) {
                this.onError((Exception)ex);
                this.engine.closeConnection(1006, ex.getMessage());
            }
            catch (final IOException ex2) {
                this.handleIOException(ex2);
            }
            this.connectReadThread = null;
        }
        catch (final InternalError internalError) {
            if (internalError.getCause() instanceof InvocationTargetException && internalError.getCause().getCause() instanceof IOException) {
                final IOException ex3 = (IOException)internalError.getCause().getCause();
                this.onWebsocketError(this.engine, (Exception)ex3);
                this.engine.closeConnection(-1, ex3.getMessage());
                return;
            }
            throw internalError;
        }
        catch (final Exception ex4) {
            this.onWebsocketError(this.engine, ex4);
            this.engine.closeConnection(-1, ex4.getMessage());
        }
    }
    
    public void send(final String s) {
        this.engine.send(s);
    }
    
    public void send(final ByteBuffer byteBuffer) {
        this.engine.send(byteBuffer);
    }
    
    public void send(final byte[] array) {
        this.engine.send(array);
    }
    
    public void sendFragmentedFrame(final Opcode opcode, final ByteBuffer byteBuffer, final boolean b) {
        this.engine.sendFragmentedFrame(opcode, byteBuffer, b);
    }
    
    public void sendFrame(final Collection<Framedata> collection) {
        this.engine.sendFrame(collection);
    }
    
    public void sendFrame(final Framedata framedata) {
        this.engine.sendFrame(framedata);
    }
    
    public void sendPing() {
        this.engine.sendPing();
    }
    
    public <T> void setAttachment(final T attachment) {
        this.engine.setAttachment(attachment);
    }
    
    public void setDnsResolver(final DnsResolver dnsResolver) {
        this.dnsResolver = dnsResolver;
    }
    
    public void setProxy(final Proxy proxy) {
        if (proxy != null) {
            this.proxy = proxy;
            return;
        }
        throw new IllegalArgumentException();
    }
    
    @Deprecated
    public void setSocket(final Socket socket) {
        if (this.socket == null) {
            this.socket = socket;
            return;
        }
        throw new IllegalStateException("socket has already been set");
    }
    
    public void setSocketFactory(final SocketFactory socketFactory) {
        this.socketFactory = socketFactory;
    }
    
    private class WebsocketWriteThread implements Runnable
    {
        final WebSocketClient this$0;
        private final WebSocketClient webSocketClient;
        
        WebsocketWriteThread(final WebSocketClient this$0, final WebSocketClient webSocketClient) {
            this.this$0 = this$0;
            this.webSocketClient = webSocketClient;
        }
        
        private void closeSocket() {
            try {
                if (this.this$0.socket != null) {
                    this.this$0.socket.close();
                }
            }
            catch (final IOException ex) {
                this.this$0.onWebsocketError(this.webSocketClient, (Exception)ex);
            }
        }
        
        private void runWriteData() throws IOException {
            try {
                while (!Thread.interrupted()) {
                    final ByteBuffer byteBuffer = (ByteBuffer)this.this$0.engine.outQueue.take();
                    this.this$0.ostream.write(byteBuffer.array(), 0, byteBuffer.limit());
                    this.this$0.ostream.flush();
                }
            }
            catch (final InterruptedException ex) {
                for (final ByteBuffer byteBuffer2 : this.this$0.engine.outQueue) {
                    this.this$0.ostream.write(byteBuffer2.array(), 0, byteBuffer2.limit());
                    this.this$0.ostream.flush();
                }
                Thread.currentThread().interrupt();
            }
        }
        
        public void run() {
            Thread.currentThread().setName("WebSocketWriteThread-" + Thread.currentThread().getId());
            while (true) {
                try {
                    try {
                        this.runWriteData();
                        this.closeSocket();
                        this.this$0.writeThread = null;
                    }
                    finally {}
                }
                catch (final IOException ex) {
                    this.this$0.handleIOException(ex);
                    continue;
                }
                break;
            }
            return;
            this.closeSocket();
            this.this$0.writeThread = null;
        }
    }
}

package org.java_websocket.client;

import java.net.InetAddress;
import java.net.URI;

public interface DnsResolver
{
    InetAddress resolve(final URI p0) throws UnknownHostException;
}

<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<androidx.appcompat.widget.ActionBarOverlayLayout android:id="@id/decor_content_parent"
                      android:fitsSystemWindows="true"
                      android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                      android:layout_height="fill_parent" xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" xmlns:macharadza="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto">
  <include layout="@layout/abc_screen_content_include" />
  <androidx.appcompat.widget.ActionBarContainer android:gravity="top"
                        android:id="@id/action_bar_container"
                        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                        android:touchscreenBlocksFocus="true"
                        android:keyboardNavigationCluster="true"
                        style="?attr/actionBarStyle">
    <androidx.appcompat.widget.Toolbar android:id="@id/action_bar"
                          android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                          android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                          macharadza:navigationContentDescription="@string/abc_action_bar_up_description"
                          style="?attr/toolbarStyle" />
    <androidx.appcompat.widget.ActionBarContextView android:theme="?attr/actionModeTheme"
                          android:id="@id/action_context_bar"
                          android:visibility="gone"
                          android:layout_width="fill_parent"
                          android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                          style="?attr/actionModeStyle" />
  </androidx.appcompat.widget.ActionBarContainer>
</androidx.appcompat.widget.ActionBarOverlayLayout>

</input-method>

                    android:propertyName="alpha" />

                    android:valueTo="0.0"

<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<selector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" xmlns:macharadza="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto">
  <item android:state_enabled="true"
        macharadza:state_liftable="true"
        macharadza:state_lifted="false">
    <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/app_bar_elevation_anim_duration"
                    android:valueTo="0.0dp"
                    android:valueType="floatType"
                    android:propertyName="elevation" />
  </item>
  <item android:state_enabled="true">
    <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/app_bar_elevation_anim_duration"
                    android:valueTo="@dimen/design_appbar_elevation"
                    android:valueType="floatType"
                    android:propertyName="elevation" />
  </item>
  <item>
    <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                    android:valueTo="0"
                    android:valueType="floatType"
                    android:propertyName="elevation" />
  </item>
</selector>

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/fragment_fade_exit.xml =====
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<objectAnimator android:interpolator="@android:anim/linear_interpolator"
                android:duration="150"
                android:valueFrom="1.0"
                android:valueTo="0.0"
                android:propertyName="alpha" xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" />

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/mtrl_btn_state_list_anim.xml =====
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<selector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
  <item android:state_enabled="true"
        android:state_pressed="true">
    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/mtrl_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_pressed_z"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="translationZ" />
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_elevation"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="elevation" />
    </set>
  </item>
  <item android:state_enabled="true"
        android:state_hovered="true">
    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/mtrl_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_hovered_z"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="translationZ" />
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_elevation"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="elevation" />
    </set>
  </item>
  <item android:state_focused="true"
        android:state_enabled="true">
    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/mtrl_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_focused_z"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="translationZ" />
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_elevation"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="elevation" />
    </set>
  </item>
  <item android:state_enabled="true">
    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/mtrl_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_z"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="translationZ"
                      android:startDelay="@integer/mtrl_btn_anim_delay_ms" />
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_elevation"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="elevation" />
    </set>
  </item>
  <item>
    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_disabled_z"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="translationZ" />
      <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                      android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_btn_disabled_elevation"
                      android:valueType="floatType"
                      android:propertyName="elevation" />
    </set>
  </item>
</selector>

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/m3_extended_fab_change_size_collapse_motion_spec.xml =====

<set xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                  android:duration="?attr/motionDurationMedium4"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="width" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                  android:duration="?attr/motionDurationMedium4"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="height" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                  android:duration="?attr/motionDurationMedium4"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="paddingStart" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                  android:duration="?attr/motionDurationMedium4"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="paddingEnd" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                  android:duration="?attr/motionDurationShort2"
                  android:startOffset="?attr/motionDurationShort1"
                  android:propertyName="labelOpacity" />
</set>

  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@interpolator/mtrl_linear_out_slow_in"
                  android:duration="200"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="opacity" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@interpolator/mtrl_linear_out_slow_in"
                  android:duration="200"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="scale" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@interpolator/mtrl_fast_out_slow_in"
                  android:duration="0"
                  android:startOffset="0"
                  android:propertyName="iconScale" />
</set>

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/m3_btn_elevated_btn_state_list_anim.xml =====
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<set xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
  <selector>
    <item android:state_enabled="true"
          android:state_hovered="true">
      <set>
        <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/m3_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_translation_z_hovered"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="translationZ" />
        <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_elevated_btn_elevation"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="elevation" />
      </set>
    </item>
    <item android:state_enabled="true">
      <set>
        <objectAnimator android:duration="@integer/m3_btn_anim_duration_ms"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_translation_z_base"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="translationZ"
                        android:startDelay="@integer/m3_btn_anim_delay_ms" />
        <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_elevated_btn_elevation"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="elevation" />
      </set>
    </item>
    <item>
      <set>
        <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_disabled_translation_z"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="translationZ" />
        <objectAnimator android:duration="0"
                        android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_btn_disabled_elevation"
                        android:valueType="floatType"
                        android:propertyName="elevation" />
      </set>
    </item>
  </selector>
</set>

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/fragment_close_enter.xml =====
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<set xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
  <set android:ordering="sequentially">
    <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@android:anim/linear_interpolator"
                    android:duration="66"
                    android:valueFrom="0.0"
                    android:valueTo="0.0"
                    android:propertyName="alpha" />
    <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@android:anim/linear_interpolator"
                    android:duration="50"
                    android:valueFrom="0.0"
                    android:valueTo="1.0"
                    android:propertyName="alpha" />
  </set>
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@anim/fragment_fast_out_extra_slow_in"
                  android:duration="300"
                  android:valueFrom="1.1"
                  android:valueTo="1.0"
                  android:propertyName="scaleX" />
  <objectAnimator android:interpolator="@anim/fragment_fast_out_extra_slow_in"
                  android:duration="300"
                  android:valueFrom="1.1"
                  android:valueTo="1.0"
                  android:propertyName="scaleY" />
</set>

  </item>
  <item android:state_enabled="true"
        macharadza:state_dragged="true">
    <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                    android:duration="?attr/motionDurationMedium4"
                    android:valueTo="@dimen/m3_card_elevated_dragged_z"

                    android:startDelay="?attr/motionDurationMedium1" />
  </item>

    <set>
      <objectAnimator android:interpolator="?attr/motionEasingEmphasizedInterpolator"
                      android:duration="?attr/motionDurationLong2"

                        android:valueTo="@dimen/mtrl_extended_fab_elevation"

    </item>

          android:state_enabled="true">

===== ./src/resources/package_1/res/animator/m3_chip_state_list_anim.xml =====
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8' ?>
<selector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
  <item android:state_enabled="true"
        android:state_selected="true"
